{"tid":1025071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2男同時追「該選誰？」一個月收45k 一個揸Benz","createTime":"2019-02-17T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T05:36:29.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f33a7fce82f8e8c40d4c404fafbef34199018e72","tid":1025071,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"女網友透過臉書「靠北男友」粉絲專頁發文指出，25歲的她最近認識2個男生，被他們同時追求，「都拿出很多誠意，兩個我也都有一點意思，可是很難抉擇。」<br />\n她說，其中一個男生大她2歲、收入約45K；另一位工作較自由，感覺是「兄弟」，開賓士。家裡的人都建議她選第一位老實男，生活安穩就好，不過她很猶豫，覺得開賓士的男生，代表在有一定的收入及能力，「也不能說他不是個好對象」。<br />\n一位網友就留言，勸他別高興太早，「畢竟大便也是一堆蒼蠅圍繞」。上千網友笑翻，紛紛留言：「這個比喻太貼切」、「真中肯啊」、「就算一個古意、一個兄弟，還是要靠自己啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190217/1518844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190217%2F1518844&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=304e8e63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190217%2F1518844&h=ebd9aadb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190217/1518844</a><br />\n<br />\n女人..到最後都係比條件"},{"pid":"d10acd7bc26bfe9bb16863f5ec572f063a4640d2","tid":1025071,"uid":738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"畢竟大便也是一堆蒼蠅圍繞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}